{"tid":345474,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"【7月新番】拳王命運 THE KING OF FIGHTERS: DESTINY集中討論","createTime":"2017-08-03T06:14:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-03T14:06:32.000Z","uid":3020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ce64f62527bedcbf1cea55bef0e6c63c37e6ea74","tid":345474,"uid":3020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T06:14:49.000Z","msg":"劇情簡介<br />\n1800年前，人類惡念凝聚而成的怪物&mdash;八歧大蛇肆虐人間，被以草薙家族為首的武術家們用三件神器封印。現代，世界綜合格斗大賽- THE KING OF FIGHTERS（簡稱KOF）召開，全世界的格鬥高手集聚南鎮。草薙家族的傳人-草薙京來到南鎮之後，他敏銳地感覺到了大蛇之力的複蘇，一切跡象表明KOF大賽背後隱藏著一個巨大的陰謀。隨著KOF大賽的召開，所有的隊伍，抱著各自的目的，漸漸被命運之手拉到了一起。而幕後的邪惡勢力已然布下了天羅地網，準備將所有的格鬥家一網打盡。正義與邪惡的對決一觸即發！<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/KW26t2D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FKW26t2D.jpg&h=8323957a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n每週四更新<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日語版<br />\n<a href=\"http://myself-bbs.com/thread-42871-1-1.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmyself-bbs.com%2Fthread-42871-1-1.html&d=hpBEV%2FeZTgeUkvmWi7ArDAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=8be3bddf\" target=\"_blank\">http://myself-bbs.com/thread-42871-1-1.html</a><br />\n<br />\n煲冬瓜版<br />\n<a href=\"https://bangumi.bilibili.com/anime/6355\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbangumi.bilibili.com%2Fanime%2F6355&d=hpBEV%2FeZTgeUkvmWi7ArDAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=470889cd\" target=\"_blank\">https://bangumi.bilibili.com/anime/6355</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上映日期：2017 年 8 月 3 日<br />\n語言版本：中日雙語<br />\n發行廠商：SNK 株式會社<br />\n官方網站：<a href=\"http://kofd.snkchina.com.cn/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fkofd.snkchina.com.cn%2F&d=hpBEV%2FeZTgeUkvmWi7ArDAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=6ac56c7d\" target=\"_blank\">http://kofd.snkchina.com.cn/</a>"},{"pid":"6e663f9db28067a016347c4308cc5e28372fb734","tid":345474,"uid":18912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T07:00:58.000Z","msg":"遊びは終わりだ！"},{"pid":"4ec75fdf82aed5